"Required. Examples: Doubao `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/responses`; OpenAI `https://api.openai.com/v1`." = "必填。示例：豆包 `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/responses`；OpenAI `https://api.openai.com/v1`。";
